snippet.title: Cute and colorful! Amber Heard legs on display at HFPA event
snippet.description:
Amber Heard turned heads at a glitzy Beverly Hills gala Thursday night. The actress, 32, arrived for the event hosted by the Hollywood Foreign Press Association in a thigh-skimming long-sleeved mini dress. Her black outfit was decorated with colorful beaded patterns and featured a collar and tiered skirt.
